рҹӨ– **Common adaptive layout mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Fixed sizes | Use `Modifier.fillMaxSize()` |
| No adaptation | Use `LocalConfiguration` |
| No orientation | Handle both orientations |
| Too many columns | Use adaptive grid |
| No padding | Add `Modifier.padding()` |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use relative sizes
Modifier.fillMaxSize()

// 2. Check screen size
val width = LocalConfiguration.current.screenWidthDp

// 3. Use adaptive layout
when {
    width < 600 -> CompactLayout()
    else -> ExpandedLayout()
}

// 4. Adaptive grid
val columns = when {
    width < 600 -> 2
    width < 840 -> 3
    else -> 4
}

// 5. Always add padding
Modifier.padding(16.dp)
